title: S12 Ep82: The Museum of Shadows.
itunes:title: The Museum of Shadows.
description:
In the sleepy town of Elmwood, Nebraska sits a 127 yr old building that is home to some of the most haunted artifacts & objects ever collected in one place. Curators Nate & Kaleigh Raterman share the strange backstories on these items and spirits that accompany them.

Nate & Kaleigh Raterman: http://www.museumofshadows.com/
